Package org.openbel.framework.core.protonetwork

Compiles a BEL document into a proto-network.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ProtoNetworkDescriptor ProtoNetworkDescriptor represents a file descriptor for a ProtoNetwork.
ProtoNetworkExternalizer ProtoNetworkExternalizer represents an externalizable ProtoNetwork.
ProtoNetworkService Compiles BEL common documents to, writes, and merges proto-networks.
 

Class Summary
BinaryProtoNetworkDescriptor BinaryProtoNetworkDescriptor represents the file descriptor for the binary-encoded proto network.
BinaryProtoNetworkExternalizer BinaryProtoNetworkExternalizer is responsible for reading a ProtoNetwork from a ProtoNetworkDescriptor and writing a ProtoNetwork to a ProtoNetworkDescriptor.
ProtoNetworkBuilder ProtoNetworkBuilder breaks down a Document into a proto network that individual identifies the following: Document header information Namespaces Which document defines which namespace Parameters Terms Which parameters are defined in which terms and in what order Statements Which document defines which statement Annotation definitions Annotation values Which statements reference which annotations
ProtoNetworkMerger ProtoNetworkMerger merges two ProtoNetwork objects together.
ProtoNetworkServiceImpl Proto-network service implementation.
TextProtoNetworkDescriptor TextProtoNetworkDescriptor represents the file descriptor for the text-encoded proto network files.
TextProtoNetworkExternalizer
